程序包 cn.ficos.Compiler.IR

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Binary
    This class represents the binary statements of IR, all operands are registers
    Branch
    This class serves as a branch node of IR
    Call
    This class serves as a call node in IR. e.g. f(1), new ...
    IRNode
    This class serves as an abstract link node of IRs
    Jump
    This class serves as a jump node of IR
    Label
    This class serves as a label in IR
    Load
    This class represent the loads in IR
    LoadAddress
    This class means loading from a label address
    LoadFromLabel
    this node is mainly used to load global variables
    LoadImm
    This class is intended to represent the "li" code in MIPS
    LoadParameter
    This class represents the loading of parameter before a function begin
    Move
    This class represents the move node in IR.
    Neg
    This class means the arithmetic negation node in IR
    New
    This class represents the new statement of IR The size counts in bytes
    Not
    This class means the bitwise not expression
    Return
    This class means the return statements of IR Note that null result means "return;"
    Store
    This class represents the store node in IR, such as 'Store $source, $address'
    StoreLabel
    this class is mainly used to represent the store of a global variable
